hes in key locations worldwide with 4,000 individual Members and Fellows. Members of the Institute are committed to maintaining the highest professional standards across the shipping industry and, as part of a professional body, members enjoy the benefits of an enhanced career in the shipping industry. Do you want to become a member? There has never been a more important time to invest in your career. Contact us to discover the Institute\'s education programmes that are available worldwide both face to face and online. To talk through your options, please feel free to book a consultation with one of our education advisors: education@ics.org.uk\nView Top Employees from Institute of Chartered Shipbrokers','http://www.ics.org.uk/','https://www.linkedin.com/company/instituteofcharteredshipbrokers/about','ics.org.uk','https://apac.commoditytradingweek.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/ics_web-2.png','yes'),('https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/D4E0BAQFc8-38owcuoQ/company-logo_200_200/0/1697717715494/commodity_thursdays_logo?e=1727308800&v=beta&t=hLDfgDGshEnXOOFVhTRaQ1trsX1_RuU32idC3TmBumo','COMMODITY THURSDAYS','CommodityThursdays','partner','https://apac.commoditytradingweek.com/',NULL,'2-10',NULL,2023,NULL,'International Trade and Development','CommodityThursdays are regular networking drinks in the shipping and commodities trading industry.','www.commoditythursdays.com','https://ch.linkedin.com/company/commodity-thursdays/about','commoditythursdays.com','https://apac.commoditytradingweek.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/image001-300x69.jpg','yes'),('https://d1hbpr09pwz0sk.cloudfront.net/logo_url/itfa-americas-amrc-3857e1d2','International Trade and Forfaiting Association','ITFA Americas (AMRC)','partner','https://apac.commoditytradingweek.com/',NULL,'201-500',NULL,1995,NULL,'Financial Services','INTERNATIONAL TRADE & FORFAITING ASSOCIATION (ITFA) is a leading non-profit organization of trade finance professionals that promotes informational exchange regarding the best practi