urnal, from Fastest Growing Eastside Companies to Washington’s Best Workplaces.   With customized, scalable, and integrated talent solutions, Simplicity is here to help you get the work done.\nView Top Employees from Simplicity Consulting','http://www.simplicityci.com','https://www.linkedin.com/company/simplicity-consulting/about','simplicityci.com','https://worldchefs.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/partner-q-industries.png','yes'),('https://d1hbpr09pwz0sk.cloudfront.net/logo_url/simplicity-ai-f6e4564f','Q industries','Simplicity AI','partner','https://www.worldchefscongress.org/',5200000,'7.0','+44 845 468 2886',2007,NULL,'Software Development','Simplicity AI Information\nSimplicity AI provides a range of advanced technical products and engineering services for test, measurement, control and automation. Customers span across a whole spectrum of industry areas including, aerospace, automotive, defence, electronics, telecoms and medical devices. Founded by Engineers with a background in test and measurement, Simplicity AI has rapidly built up a reputation for successfully delivering solutions. With particular expertise in developing automatic test and measurement software which is built around the industry standard platforms, Simplicity AI works with test equipment and tools providers such as National Instruments, Agilent and Pickering Interfaces. The product offering includes Tequra, a software suite for test and measurement applications allowing users to develop high-quality software faster, simplify support and maintenance, and facilitate continuous improvement. Technical services can be tailored to fit the needs of customers. The scale of offering can range from short training and consulting activities, through to large turn-key system delivery and long term partnering relationships. Simplicity AI is an ISO 9001:2008 Certified Organisation. Find us on: www.facebook.com/simplicityai plus.google.com/+SimplicityAIcouk www.twitter.com/simplicityai www.facebook.com/te